WHILE the entertainment industry is still coming to terms with the death of Joe &ldquo;S&rsquo;dumo&rdquo; Mafela, the football fraternity is mourning the death of legendary Petrus Molemela who died this morning.Molemela, who was due to turn 84 next month, succumbed to death after a long illness. News about the death of the old man previously known as &ldquo;Whitehead&rdquo; because of the colour of his hair, was confirmed by Bloemfontein Celtic CEO, Khumbulani Konco, yesterday.